statement.paragraphs:
  Given a set of vectors $S=\{\mathbf{u}_{1},\,\mathbf{u}_{2},\,\mathbf{u}_{3},\,\ldots,\,\mathbf{u}_{n}\}$, an equality of the form
\begin{align*}
